{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-tangfeng-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-tangfeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-tangfeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·唐風·001.1", "text_original": "蟋蟀在堂，歲聿其莫。今我不樂，日月其除。無已大康，職思其居。好樂無荒，良士瞿瞿。", "text_normalized": "蟋蟀在堂，歲聿其莫。今我不樂，日月其除。無已大康，職思其居。好樂無荒，良士瞿瞿。", "notes": "蟋蟀 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-tangfeng-001__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-tangfeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-tangfeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·唐風·001.2", "text_original": "蟋蟀在堂，歲聿其逝。今我不樂，日月其邁。無已大康，職思其外。好樂無荒，良士蹶蹶。", "text_normalized": "蟋蟀在堂，歲聿其逝。今我不樂，日月其邁。無已大康，職思其外。好樂無荒，良士蹶蹶。", "notes": "蟋蟀 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-tangfeng-001__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-tangfeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-tangfeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·唐風·001.3", "text_original": "蟋蟀在堂，役車其休。今我不樂，日月其慆。無已大康，職思其憂。好樂無荒，良士休休。", "text_normalized": "蟋蟀在堂，役車其休。今我不樂，日月其慆。無已大康，職思其憂。好樂無荒，良士休休。", "notes": "蟋蟀 Chinese stanza 3."}
